title: Lafayette 41 Poquoson 19: Extra highlights
text:
Lafayette 41 Poquoson 19: Extra highlights Rams improve to 7-0 and hoping to make it three straight years of undefeated regular seasons. Post to Facebook Lafayette 41 Poquoson 19: Extra highlights Rams improve to 7-0 and hoping to make it three straight years of undefeated regular seasons.  //on.wvec.com/1RLnylR   Lafayette 41 Poquoson 19: Extra highlights The Rams improve to 7-0 with their 41-19 win.   11:03 p.m. EDT October 15, 2015 Lafayette vs Poquoson   
In the buildup to the game, Poquoson was seen as the biggest threat on the schedule for Lafayette this season. Threat denied. Lafayette dominated most of the night on the way to a 41-19 win. 
Caleb Kraegenbrink ran for 194 yards and two touchdowns for the Rams. 
Lafayette improves to (7-0) and is well on their way to a third straight undefeated regular season.
